Hello,

I wrote a little program to convert  BibTeX files to HTML documents (I
know there is  already a program of that  kind, "bib2html", but it  is
full  of limitations   and  bugs).  bibtex2html   is 100% written   in
Objective  Caml, and so  should be fully   portable. You can find more
details and source code at the following URL:

	http://www.ens-lyon.fr/~jcfillia/bibtex2html.en.html

Don't hesitate to send me comments (and bug reports).
-- 
Jean-Christophe FILLIATRE
  email: Jean-Christophe.Filliatre@ens-lyon.fr
  WWW  : http://www.ens-lyon.fr/~jcfillia


